## 🔧 Vue 重构技巧

### 代码异味识别

**组件过大**:
```vue
<!-- ❌ 代码异味：组件过大（>500 行） -->
<template>
  <!-- 200 行模板 -->
</template>

<script setup lang="ts">
  // 300 行代码
</script>

<!-- ✅ 修复：拆分组件 -->
<!-- Parent.vue -->
<template>
  <UserProfile />
  <UserSettings />
  <UserActivity />
</template>
```

**过长方法**:
```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
// ❌ 代码异味：方法过长
const processUserData = () => {
  // 100 行代码
}

// ✅ 修复：拆分方法
const validateUserData = () => { ... }
const normalizeUserData = () => { ... }
const saveUserData = () => { ... }
</script>
```

**重复代码**:
```vue
<!-- ❌ 代码异味：重复代码 -->
<!-- Component1.vue -->
<template>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>{{ title }}</h3>
    <p>{{ description }}</p>
  </div>
</template>

<!-- Component2.vue -->
<template>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>{{ title }}</h3>
    <p>{{ description }}</p>
  </div>
</template>

<!-- ✅ 修复：提取公共组件 -->
<!-- BaseCard.vue -->
<template>
  <div class="card">
    <h3><slot name="title"></slot></h3>
    <p><slot name="description"></slot></p>
  </div>
</template>
```

**Props 过多**:
```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
// ❌ 代码异味：Props 过多（>5 个）
interface Props {
  userId: number
  userName: string
  userEmail: string
  userAge: number
  userRole: string
  isActive: boolean
}

// ✅ 修复：使用对象 Props
interface Props {
  user: {
    id: number
    name: string
    email: string
    age: number
    role: string
    isActive: boolean
  }
}
</script>
```

---

### 重构模式

**提取组件**:
```vue
<!-- ❌ 修复前：大组件 -->
<template>
  <div>
    <header>...</header>
    <nav>...</nav>
    <main>...</main>
    <footer>...</footer>
  </div>
</template>

<!-- ✅ 修复后：拆分组件 -->
<template>
  <div>
    <AppHeader />
    <AppNav />
    <AppMain />
    <AppFooter />
  </div>
</template>
```

**提取 Composable**:
```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
// ❌ 修复前：逻辑混在组件中
const count = ref(0)
const increment = () => count.value++
const decrement = () => count.value--

const users = ref([])
const fetchUsers = async () => { ... }
const addUser = (user) => { ... }

// ✅ 修复后：提取 Composable
// composables/useCounter.ts
export function useCounter() {
  const count = ref(0)
  const increment = () => count.value++
  const decrement = () => count.value--
  return { count, increment, decrement }
}

// composables/useUsers.ts
export function useUsers() {
  const users = ref([])
  const fetchUsers = async () => { ... }
  const addUser = (user) => { ... }
  return { users, fetchUsers, addUser }
}
</script>
```

**替换条件渲染**:
```vue
<!-- ❌ 修复前：复杂条件 -->
<template>
  <div v-if="userRole === 'admin'">
    <AdminPanel />
  </div>
  <div v-else-if="userRole === 'manager'">
    <ManagerPanel />
  </div>
  <div v-else-if="userRole === 'user'">
    <UserPanel />
  </div>
  <div v-else>
    <GuestPanel />
  </div>
</template>

<!-- ✅ 修复后：动态组件 -->
<template>
  <component :is="panelComponent" />
</template>

<script setup lang="ts">
const panelComponent = computed(() => {
  const map = {
    admin: AdminPanel,
    manager: ManagerPanel,
    user: UserPanel,
    guest: GuestPanel
  }
  return map[userRole.value] || GuestPanel
})
</script>
```

