## 🐛 Vue Bug 修复

### 常见 Bug 模式

**直接修改 Props**:
```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
interface Props {
  count: number
}

const props = defineProps<Props>()

// ❌ Bug：直接修改 Props
const increment = () => {
  props.count++
}

// ✅ 修复：使用 Emits
const emit = defineEmits<{
  (e: 'update:count', value: number): void
}>()

const increment = () => {
  emit('update:count', props.count + 1)
}
</script>
```

**响应式丢失**:
```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
// ❌ Bug：解构失去响应性
const state = reactive({ count: 0 })
const { count } = state

// ✅ 修复：使用 toRefs
const state = reactive({ count: 0 })
const { count } = toRefs(state)

// 或使用 ref
const count = ref(0)
</script>
```

**v-if 和 v-for 同元素**:
```vue
<!-- ❌ Bug：v-if 和 v-for 同元素 -->
<template>
  <li v-for="user in users" v-if="user.isActive">
    {{ user.name }}
  </li>
</template>

<!-- ✅ 修复：使用计算属性 -->
<template>
  <li v-for="user in activeUsers" :key="user.id">
    {{ user.name }}
  </li>
</template>

<script setup lang="ts">
const activeUsers = computed(() => 
  users.value.filter(user => user.isActive)
)
</script>
```

**缺少 Key 属性**:
```vue
<!-- ❌ Bug：缺少 Key -->
<template>
  <div v-for="user in users">
    {{ user.name }}
  </div>
</template>

<!-- ✅ 修复：添加 Key -->
<template>
  <div v-for="user in users" :key="user.id">
    {{ user.name }}
  </div>
</template>
```

---

### Pinia 特定修复

**State 直接修改**:
```typescript
// ❌ Bug：直接修改 State
const userStore = useUserStore()
userStore.currentUser.name = 'New Name'

// ✅ 修复：使用 Action
const userStore = useUserStore()
userStore.updateUserName('New Name')
```

**Store 解构失去响应性**:
```typescript
// ❌ Bug：直接解构
const userStore = useUserStore()
const { currentUser } = userStore

// ✅ 修复：使用 storeToRefs
import { storeToRefs } from 'pinia'
const userStore = useUserStore()
const { currentUser } = storeToRefs(userStore)
```

---

## 🚀 Vue 性能优化

### 性能问题识别

**不必要的组件重渲染**:
```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
// ❌ 性能问题：父组件更新导致子组件重渲染
const parentData = ref(0)
const updateParent = () => parentData.value++

// ✅ 修复：使用 shallowRef 或 memo
import { shallowRef } from 'vue'
const parentData = shallowRef(0)
</script>
```

**大列表渲染**:
```vue
<!-- ❌ 性能问题：渲染大列表 -->
<template>
  <div v-for="item in largeList" :key="item.id">
    {{ item.name }}
  </div>
</template>

<!-- ✅ 修复：虚拟滚动 -->
<template>
  <RecycleScroller
    :items="largeList"
    :item-size="50"
    key-field="id"
  >
    <template #default="{ item }">
      <div>{{ item.name }}</div>
    </template>
  </RecycleScroller>
</template>
```

**计算属性缓存**:
```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
// ❌ 性能问题：方法每次渲染都执行
const filteredUsers = () => {
  return users.value.filter(user => user.isActive)
}

// ✅ 修复：使用计算属性
const filteredUsers = computed(() => {
  return users.value.filter(user => user.isActive)
})
</script>
```

---

### 性能优化技巧

**懒加载组件**:
```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
// ❌ 修复前：同步加载
import HeavyComponent from '@/components/HeavyComponent.vue'

// ✅ 修复后：懒加载
const HeavyComponent = defineAsyncComponent(
  () => import('@/components/HeavyComponent.vue')
)
</script>
```

**路由懒加载**:
```typescript
// ❌ 修复前：同步加载路由
const routes = [
  {
    path: '/dashboard',
    component: Dashboard
  }
]

// ✅ 修复后：懒加载路由
const routes = [
  {
    path: '/dashboard',
    component: () => import('@/views/Dashboard.vue')
  }
]
```

**图片懒加载**:
```vue
<!-- ❌ 修复前：立即加载 -->
<img :src="largeImage" />

<!-- ✅ 修复后：懒加载 -->
<img loading="lazy" :src="largeImage" />
```

