## 🔒 Vue 安全修复

### 常见安全漏洞

**XSS 修复**:
```vue
<!-- ❌ 安全漏洞：v-html 滥用 -->
<template>
  <div v-html="userInput"></div>
</template>

<!-- ✅ 修复：使用文本插值 -->
<template>
  <div>{{ userInput }}</div>
</template>

<!-- ✅ 必须使用 v-html 时 -->
<template>
  <div v-html="sanitizeHtml(userInput)"></div>
</template>

<script setup lang="ts">
import DOMPurify from 'dompurify'

const sanitizeHtml = (html: string) => {
  return DOMPurify.sanitize(html)
}
</script>
```

**API Token 泄露**:
```typescript
// ❌ 安全漏洞：Token 存储在 localStorage
localStorage.setItem('token', token)

// ✅ 修复：使用 HttpOnly Cookie
// 后端设置 HttpOnly Cookie
// 前端自动发送
```

**路由守卫缺失**:
```typescript
// ❌ 安全漏洞：缺少路由守卫
const routes = [
  {
    path: '/admin',
    component: AdminPanel
  }
]

// ✅ 修复：添加路由守卫
const routes = [
  {
    path: '/admin',
    component: AdminPanel,
    meta: { requiresAuth: true, requiresRole: 'admin' }
  }
]

router.beforeEach((to, from, next) => {
  if (to.meta.requiresAuth && !isAuthenticated) {
    next('/login')
  } else if (to.meta.requiresRole && !hasRole(to.meta.requiresRole)) {
    next('/unauthorized')
  } else {
    next()
  }
})
```

