## 🔧 修复工具

### 自动化工具

**代码质量**:
```bash
# ESLint 检查
eslint src/ --ext .vue,.ts

# Prettier 格式化
prettier --write src/

# Vue TypeScript 检查
vue-tsc --noEmit

# 类型检查
tsc --noEmit
```

**自动修复**:
```bash
# ESLint 自动修复
eslint src/ --ext .vue,.ts --fix

# Prettier 格式化
prettier --write src/
```

---

### CI/CD 集成

**GitHub Actions**:
```yaml
name: Code Quality
on: [pull_request]
jobs:
  lint:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v2
      - name: Set up Node.js
        uses: actions/setup-node@v2
        with:
          node-version: '18'
      - name: Install dependencies
        run: npm ci
      - name: Run linters
        run: |
          npm run lint
          npm run type-check
```

